    <mods:description>Eldest daughter of Robert Moffat. Married David Livingstone in 1845. Accompanied him on his early journeys, but sent to England 1852. Returned with him in 1858, but could not go beyond Cape Town. Rejoined him 30 January 1862, and died 27 April 1862.</mods:description>
